tool_description: Extract references found in the Financial Conduct Authority Handbook.
name: FCA Handbook Extraction
title: FCA Handbook Extraction

api_list.name: Extract
api_list.description: Will find references to FCA Handbook items, their position within the text and a link to the item in the handbook.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://fca-handbook-extraction.p.rapidapi.com/api/Extract/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "fca-handbook-extraction.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
